{"tid":371353,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[組團]單車去西藏","createTime":"2017-08-23T15:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T02:08:05.000Z","uid":95872,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a95958622e2e2c4ef412cc5be0892bc58f4c416","tid":371353,"uid":95872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的. <br />\n來緊小弟出年Grad, 想藉呢個最後的暑假, 係5-7月呢段時間, 完成一樣此生難忘的事情, 但遺憾地小弟身邊冇人打算陪我一齊癲。<br />\n<br />\n小弟有兩有plan。<br />\nPlan 1) 由香港踩單車去西藏, 時間為兩個月, 大約4000km.<br />\nPlan 2) 如果到時只有一個月既時間, 咁就會改為成都出發踩去西藏, 大約2000km.<br />\n<br />\n單車方面, 小弟亦冇打算突登去買架單車, 因此會去堔圳 OR 成都租。<br />\n<br />\n計劃初步係咁, 因為要一定既時間去準備(特別係體能), 所以提早開POST組團。<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇邊位巴打有興趣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣既就直接pm我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af1eb1f90c6c73c50512eb99d66ac5268226c02","tid":371353,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"加油啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f73330efb390c49660b3aee7aff4e9ec0650ef2","tid":371353,"uid":95872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果最後冇人JOIN, 我諗我會獨自出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1211b21c3db946f6eb1683d00567494fb6dcbad","tid":371353,"uid":113465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加油啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\"